  "Tathāgato",
  "Tiṇṇo samuddaṃ paṇḍito.",
  "Tvaṃ dānaṃ dassasi.\\nTumhe dānaṃ dassatha.",
  "Tvaṃ kiṃ passasi?\\nAhaṃ rukkhaṃ passāmi.",
  "Upāsako bhikkhū bhojeti.",
  "Upāsako dānaṃ dadeyya.\\nUpāsakā dānāni dadeyyuṃ.",
  "Upāsako vihāraṃ agami.\\nUpāsakā vihāraṃ agamiṃsu.",
  "Upāsakā pupphehi Buddhaṃ pūjenti.",
  "Vanitā sālaṃ gacchati.\\nVanitāyo sālaṃ gacchanti.",
  "Vānarā rukkhaṃ āruyha phalāni khādanti.",
  "Vāṇijo kassakassa ajaṃ dadāti.\\nVāṇijā kassakānaṃ aje dadanti.",
  "Vāṇijo kassakaṃ paharati / Vāṇijā kassake paharanti",
